gateways expose service_listen_address on unix socket
==> reason: free version of nginx requires restart if upstream becomes unavailable

nginx configured like this:
  location ~ ^/roq/gateway/([\w-]*)/(.*)$ {
    proxy_pass http://unix:/run/roq/service/$1.sock:/$2;
  }
this allows us to access any gateway using /roq/gateway/<name>/... URLs

MISSING
- ansible should install a static file (json) with list of available gateway names
